{"tid":596051,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[學術交流]點解美國咁多黑人","createTime":"2018-03-17T09:11:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-17T12:07:08.000Z","uid":76922,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c409fdf8b96a9789112e3da672ec50b9c9a0c3ff","tid":596051,"uid":76922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T09:11:04.000Z","msg":"最近屎忽痕 上網搵下資料睇下點解美國咁多黑人<br />\n但奈何搵到o既都係一堆種族主義 黑人歧視之類o既野 <br />\n但究竟美國做左啲咩令到美國會咁多黑人 <br />\n有咩政策 有咩利誘令到黑人係美國 甚至其他非黑人國家都開始多黑人 <br />\n本身美國人係白人黎嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家討論<br />\n冇歧視成份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0beee6e1f0b7c65e135b5eeef366cd0b7e249704","tid":596051,"uid":162043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T09:19:28.000Z","msg":"曬到變黑"},{"pid":"dd8fdb700073f2c6772b650d3e5ffa8b88ffeba6","tid":596051,"uid":114704,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T09:20:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a770e0963343806a34ae8df8274838f274f4e893","tid":596051,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T09:20:39.000Z","msg":"本身美國人係呢啲<br />\n[img]<a href=\"http://www.offthegridnews.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/native-americans-1.jpg[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.offthegridnews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F11%2Fnative-americans-1.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=VYmZ4YKFRU2EKBODof7%2B0P7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=ebf86998\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.offthegridnews.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/native-americans-1.jpg[/img]</a>"},{"pid":"cb2dbb0c511fa619ccba25e8f46583a5bd02fe8f","tid":596051,"uid":148541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T09:22:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"074ec8eab639817bb0214e820ec90f8a55e72d4e","tid":596051,"uid":35317,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T09:26:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://med